      "content": "You can't just \"care\" about DEI, you have to actively work towards it. Here are some caption options that acknowledge your commitment to creating a welcoming space:\n\nOption 1: \"At [Your Coffee Shop], we're dedicated to brewing more than just great coffee - we're committed to brewing a more inclusive community. Join us in celebrating our diversity and promoting equity for all.\"\n\nOption 2: \"We believe that everyone deserves a cup of coffee, regardless of their background or identity. Our commitment to DEI is more than just a slogan - it's a promise to create a space where everyone feels seen and valued.\"\n\nOption 3: \"Our coffee may be small-batch, but our commitment to DEI is anything but. We're working hard to create a culture of inclusion and equity, and we invite you to join us on this journey.\"\n\nOption 4: \"At [Your Coffee Shop], we're not just serving coffee - we're serving a vision of a more just and equitable world. Join us in celebrating our diversity and promoting a culture of inclusion.\"",
